---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Words Containing MU — Scrabble Word List & Strategy"
  description="Complete list of Scrabble words containing MU with scores, definitions, and strategic tips. Master MU words for better Scrabble plays."
  keywords="scrabble words containing mu, mu words scrabble, words with mu, scrabble mu word list, mu scrabble strategy"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Words Containing MU — Scrabble Word List & Strategy",
    "description": "Complete list of Scrabble words containing MU with scores, definitions, and strategic tips.",
    "datePublished": "2026-06-15",
    "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com", "url": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com" },
    "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "ScrabbleWordsFinder.com" },
    "mainEntityOfPage": { "@type": "WebPage", "@id": "https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/words-containing-mu" }
  })} />

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the highest-scoring MU words in Scrabble?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Top MU words include MULCHING (16 pts), COMMUNAL (14 pts), FORMULA (12 pts), MUSEUM (10 pts), and MUTUAL (8 pts). MU appears in 350+ valid Scrabble words." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "How many Scrabble words contain MU?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Around 350 valid Scrabble words contain MU. Common examples include MUCH, MUST, MUSIC, MULE, FORMULA, MUSEUM, COMMUNITY, and MUTUAL." } },
      { "@type": "Question", "name": "What strategy works best with MU tiles?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "MU is moderately productive with 350+ words. The MU- prefix (MUCH, MUST, MULE, MUSIC) gives reliable short plays. The -MUL pattern (FORMULA, TUMULT) and -MUN endings (COMMUNE, COMMUNITY) build toward bingos. MULCHING (16 pts) and COMMUNAL (14 pts) are top targets." } }
    ]
  })} />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1">
        <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a>
        <span class="mx-1">›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-300">Letter Pair Content</span>
      </nav>

      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Words Containing MU — Scrabble Word List & Strategy</h1>

      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <span>4 min read</span>
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">MU is a moderately productive letter pair appearing in around 350 valid Scrabble words. From common plays like MUCH and MUST to premium targets like MULCHING (16 pts) and COMMUNAL (14 pts), MU offers solid scoring across multiple word patterns. The MU- prefix provides strong openers, while the -MUN and -MUL patterns extend naturally into longer words.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top MU Words by Score</h2>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border border-gray-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
          <thead class="bg-gray-800">
            <tr>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">#</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Word</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Points</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold text-gray-300">Definition</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-800">
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">1</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MULCHING</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">16</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Covering soil with material</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">2</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">COMMUNAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">14</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Shared by a community</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">3</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">FORMULA</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">12</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A set expression</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">4</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MUCH</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">11</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A large amount</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">5</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MUSCLE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Body tissue for movement</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MUSEUM</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A place for exhibits</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">7</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MUSK</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A strong scent</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">8</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MUSIC</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Organized sound</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">9</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MUTUAL</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">8</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">Shared between parties</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">10</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MULE</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">A hybrid animal</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-900"><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">11</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-white font-medium">MUST</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-blue-400">6</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-400">An obligation</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">~350</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid MU words</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">10 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Average score</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">Moderate</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Pair frequency</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy Tips for MU Words</h2>

      <p>MU- prefix words (MUCH, MUST, MULE, MUSIC, MUSK) provide reliable short plays throughout the game. The -MUN pattern (COMMUNE, SUMMON) and -MUL endings (FORMULA, TUMULT) build toward 7-letter bingos. MUCH (11 pts) scores well due to the H and C tiles. Pair MU with K for strong returns — MUSK (10 pts) is an efficient play that deploys the 5-point K tile.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MULCHING</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">16 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">COMMUNAL</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">14 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">FORMULA</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">12 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MUCH</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">11 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MUSCLE</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">10 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">MUSK</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">10 pts</span></span>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">🎯 Key Takeaway</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">MU provides <span class="text-white font-medium">~350 valid words</span> with solid scoring. MULCHING (16 pts) and COMMUNAL (14 pts) are premium targets. MUCH (11 pts) and MUSK (10 pts) are efficient short plays that use the high-value H and K tiles alongside this pair.</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a href="/blog/words-containing-qu" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Words Containing QU — Essential Scrabble Q Words</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/words-with-multiple-vowels" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Words With Multiple Vowels — Scrabble Vowel Dumps</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/four-letter-words-every-player-should-know" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Four-Letter Words Every Scrabble Player Should Know</span></a>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-blue-800/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">🔤 Find every MU word from your tiles — instant results, no signup</p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-400 text-gray-950 text-sm font-semibold transition-colors">Open Word Finder →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Back to all articles</a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
